      "span_text": "Of the 2,428 individuals, G6PD phenotypes (fluorescent spot test) and genotypes for the 3 most common G6PD variants (Mahidol, Viengchan, and Canton) had already been obtained for 925 individuals, including 415 male individuals  ."
